name: isSubset
signature: { <A>(that: HashSet<A>): (self: HashSet<A>) => boolean; <A>(self: HashSet<A>, that: HashSet<A>): boolean; }
description:
Returns `true` if and only if every element in the this `HashSet` is an
element of the second set,
*NOTE: the hash and equal of both sets must be the same. Time complexity analysis is of `O(n)`
